            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Usability Testing</h3>
                <p>Evaluated how easily users can navigate through the portfolio sections and project phases.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Regression Testing</h3>
                <p>Retested fixed defects to confirm that the website still works correctly after changes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

