    <section class="phase-section">
        <h2>Defect Reports</h2>

        <div class="bug-grid">
            <div class="bug-card">
                <div class="bug-header">
                    <h3>BUG-001: Dropdown Menu Issue</h3>
                    <span class="status closed">Closed</span>
                </div>

                <p><strong>Type:</strong> UI / Usability Bug</p>
                <p><strong>Severity:</strong> Medium</p>
                <p><strong>Priority:</strong> High</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> Fixed and Closed</p>
                <p><strong>Retest Result:</strong> Passed</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> The project phases dropdown disappeared before the user could select a phase.</p>

                <p><strong>Steps to Reproduce:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Hover over the Projects menu</li>
                    <li>Move the cursor to select a phase</li>
                    <li>The submenu disappears</li>
                </ul>

                <p><strong>Expected Result:</strong> Dropdown remains visible until the user selects a phase.</p>
                <p><strong>Actual Result:</strong> Dropdown closed before selection.</p>
                <p><strong>Root Cause:</strong> CSS hover behavior and submenu positioning issue.</p>
                <p><strong>Fix:</strong> Adjusted submenu position and improved hover behavior in CSS.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bug-card">
                <div class="bug-header">
                    <h3>BUG-002: UI/UX Page Not Found</h3>
                    <span class="status closed">Closed</span>
                </div>

                <p><strong>Type:</strong> Functional / Routing Bug</p>
                <p><strong>Severity:</strong> High</p>
                <p><strong>Priority:</strong> High</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> Fixed and Closed</p>
                <p><strong>Retest Result:</strong> Passed</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> The UI/UX phase page did not open correctly.</p>

                <p><strong>Steps to Reproduce:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Open the Projects dropdown</li>
                    <li>Select UI/UX Design phase</li>
                    <li>The page fails to open</li>
                </ul>

                <p><strong>Expected Result:</strong> UI/UX phase page opens successfully.</p>
                <p><strong>Actual Result:</strong> Page not found error appeared.</p>
                <p><strong>Root Cause:</strong> MVC View name did not match the Controller action.</p>
                <p><strong>Fix:</strong> Renamed the View to match the MVC routing structure.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

